&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0pt? 0in **Zowie**?MARGIN:&gt;&lt;SPAN ?Century Gothic?? 10pt; **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE: FONT-FAMILY:&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN ?Century Gothic?? 10pt; **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE: FONT-FAMILY:&gt;Currently on Test server – This means that the development team has implement this item and it’s currently on test server, watch for future updates for implementation on the live servers.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0pt? 0in **Zowie**?MARGIN:&gt;&lt;SPAN ?Century Gothic?? 10pt; **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE: FONT-FAMILY:&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN 10pt; **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE: FONT-FAMILY: Verdana?&gt;Waiting for community feedback&amp;nbsp;– This means we don’t have enough information to make any type of decision on how to implement.&amp;nbsp; Threads will be started by me to get your feedback.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN ?Century Gothic?? 10pt; **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE: FONT-FAMILY:&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
