&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;FONT face="Courier New"&gt;1) &lt;FONT color=#0000ff&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;Add more throwing items for rogues to use. &lt;FONT color=#0000ff&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;(currently being evaluated) - Most likely this will be considered as part of the class re-envisioning&amp;nbsp;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;- Lack of itemisation is preventing good use of the Deadly Aim discipline we received with OoW. &lt;BR&gt;- Throwing items must be summoned in order to be practical, along the lines of Ton Po's Mystical Pouch from Time. &lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;2) &lt;FONT color=#0000ff&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;Enhance the Nerves of Steel AA so that it functions against single target spells as well (as is implied by the current description) or, failing that, refund the AA. &lt;FONT color=#0000ff&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;(currently being evaluated)&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;BR&gt;- This ability is also bugged. Hide is incorrectly being broken by AE spells that have been resisted and the description is wrong. &lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;3) &lt;FONT color=#0000ff&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;Improved critical hit AAs such as Veterans Wrath should apply to backstab. &lt;FONT color=#0000ff&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;(currently being evaluated)&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;BR&gt;4) Minimum bs damage should scale with weapon / Scale Chaotic Stab with weapon damage. &lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;(currently being evaluated&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;) - Most likely this will be considered as part of the class re-envisioning &lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;5) Slightly increase the availability of tradable and single group weapons that allow more casual, unguilded, and/or non raiding rogues to stay relatively viable. &lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;(currently being evaluated) &lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;6) &lt;FONT color=#0000ff&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;Assassin’s Strike is still not effective enough for the endurance cost. The endurance cost should be reduced to make it more in line with similar abilities of other classes. &lt;FONT color=#0000ff&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;(currently being evaluated)&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;BR&gt;7) Shroud of Stealth should make it so monsters see a rogue much more rarely then it does &lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;(currently being &lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;evaluated) - Most likely this will be considered as part of the class re-envisioning &lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;8)&amp;nbsp;Make poisons easier to use and less prohibitive in terms of time investment. Some suggestions of how to achieve this are: &lt;FONT color=#0000ff&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;(currently being evaluated) - Most likely this will be considered as part of the class re-envisioning &lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;BR&gt;- Implement some form of endless poison or poison conservation AA. &lt;BR&gt;- Increase the drop rate of poison ingredients or make them purchaseable at a reasonable cost. &lt;BR&gt;- Increase the yield of poisons per combine. &lt;BR&gt;- Dramatically increase the yield of poisons per combine, making the poisons yielded no rent. &lt;BR&gt;- Make old world poisons stackable. &lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;9)&amp;nbsp;Add more +backstab damage items at all levels of play.&amp;nbsp; &lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;(currently being evaluated)&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;10)&lt;FONT color=#0000ff&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; Re-evaluate the focus effects on rogue armour sets from Qvic onwards.&amp;nbsp; &lt;FONT color=#0000ff&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;(currently being evaluated)&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;BR&gt;- The armour sets appear to have been copy/pasted a lot rather than individually tailored for each class. This does not work well for rogues because our desires are so specialised. &lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;BUGS:&amp;nbsp;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;- Fix the interaction (bug) between sneak/hide and Bard invis. This bug is not always specific to Bard songs. Some rogues have experienced the breaking of hide when a cast invis spell fades. &lt;FONT color=#ff6600&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;**Fixed**&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;BR&gt;- &lt;FONT color=#0000ff&gt;*New*&lt;/FONT&gt; Assassins Feint (DoN discipline) does not appear to be functioning correctly.&amp;nbsp;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;- Dev knows of this and it is slated to be fixed&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;BR&gt;- &lt;FONT color=#0000ff&gt;*Sort of new*&lt;/FONT&gt; Nerves of Steel (AA) is not functioning correctly (see above) &lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;-&amp;nbsp; &lt;FONT color=#0000ff&gt;*New*&lt;/FONT&gt; Sneak / Hide across zones appears to be bugged and fail sometimes.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;p&gt;Message Edited by Kytherea on &lt;span class=date_text&gt;04-04-2005&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=time_text&gt;10:26 AM&lt;/span&gt;</description>
